   _ There will be no foreign sovereignity over any part of the Land
of Israel;
   _ No Palestinian state shall come into being in the Land of
Israel;
   _ And there shall be no negotiations with the terrorist
organizations, the PLO.
   Likud representatives are obliged to act in the government and
the Knesset in accordance with the principles included in the prime
minister's announcement and in accordance with the Likud platform.
